snippet.title: Cat Quest - Official Launch Trailer - iOS, Steam
snippet.description:
OUT NOW on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/593280/Cat_Quest/

The official launch trailer for iOS and Steam! Cat Quest is an open world RPG...with cats!
Releasing August 8th on Steam, and August 10th on iOS!

Find out more at:
https://www.facebook.com/catquestgame/
https://thegentlebros.com/catquest/

Follow us on Twitter @TheGentlebros
https://twitter.com/TheGentlebros

Subscribe to the mailing list and get notified when it releases!
http://thegentlebros.com/catquest/#subscribe

Gameplay shown was captured using the PC version of Cat Quest!
